              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-heading text-primary text-lg font-semibold">Innovación</h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral leading-relaxed">
          Buscamos constantemente nuevas formas de resolver problemas legales de manera creativa y
          efectiva.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-neutral/5 p-6 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="bg-primary/10 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="text-primary h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
